Neon Anime API — Documentation

Base URL

https://nt-animes.onrender.com


⸻

1. Search Anime

Search for anime by title.

Endpoint

GET /search

Query Parameters

Parameter	Required	Description
keyword	Yes	Anime title

Example

https://nt-animes.onrender.com/search?keyword=naruto

Response

{
  "keyword": "naruto",
    "results": [
        {
              "title": "Naruto",
                    "url": "naruto",
                          "thumbnail": "https://image-url.jpg",
                                "episodes": {
                                        "sub": 220,
                                                "dub": 220,
                                                        "total": 220
                                                              },
                                                                    "type": "TV"
                                                                        }
                                                                          ]
                                                                          }

                                                                          url is the anime slug used in other endpoints.

                                                                          ⸻

                                                                          2. Trending Anime

                                                                          Returns currently trending anime.

                                                                          Endpoint

                                                                          GET /trending

                                                                          Example

                                                                          https://nt-animes.onrender.com/trending

                                                                          Response

                                                                          {
                                                                            "results": [
                                                                                {
                                                                                      "title": "Solo Leveling",
                                                                                            "url": "solo-leveling",
                                                                                                  "thumbnail": "https://image-url.jpg",
                                                                                                        "episodes": {
                                                                                                                "sub": 12,
                                                                                                                        "dub": 12,
                                                                                                                                "total": 12
                                                                                                                                      },
                                                                                                                                            "type": "TV"
                                                                                                                                                }
                                                                                                                                                  ]
                                                                                                                                                  }


                                                                                                                                                  ⸻

                                                                                                                                                  3. Anime Metadata

                                                                                                                                                  Returns full anime information.

                                                                                                                                                  Endpoint

                                                                                                                                                  GET /metadata

                                                                                                                                                  Query Parameters

                                                                                                                                                  Parameter	Required	Description
                                                                                                                                                  anime	Yes	Anime slug

                                                                                                                                                  Example

                                                                                                                                                  https://nt-animes.onrender.com/metadata?anime=naruto

                                                                                                                                                  Response

                                                                                                                                                  {
                                                                                                                                                    "title": "Naruto",
                                                                                                                                                      "rating": "8.3",
                                                                                                                                                        "quality": "HD",
                                                                                                                                                          "has_sub": true,
                                                                                                                                                            "has_dub": true,
                                                                                                                                                              "description": "A young ninja strives to become Hokage.",
                                                                                                                                                                "type": "TV",
                                                                                                                                                                  "source": "Manga",
                                                                                                                                                                    "premiered": "Fall 2002",
                                                                                                                                                                      "date_aired": "Oct 2002 - Feb 2007",
                                                                                                                                                                        "broadcast": "Thursdays",
                                                                                                                                                                          "status": "Finished Airing",
                                                                                                                                                                            "genres": ["Action", "Adventure"],
                                                                                                                                                                              "mal_rating": "8.3",
                                                                                                                                                                                "duration": "23 min",
                                                                                                                                                                                  "total_episodes": "220",
                                                                                                                                                                                    "studios": ["Studio Pierrot"],
                                                                                                                                                                                      "producers": ["TV Tokyo"],
                                                                                                                                                                                        "thumbnail": "https://image-url.jpg"
                                                                                                                                                                                        }


                                                                                                                                                                                        ⸻

                                                                                                                                                                                        4. Watch Episode (Streaming)

                                                                                                                                                                                        Streams anime video.

                                                                                                                                                                                        Endpoint

                                                                                                                                                                                        GET /watch/:anime/:episode

                                                                                                                                                                                        Parameters

                                                                                                                                                                                        Parameter	Description
                                                                                                                                                                                        anime	Anime slug
                                                                                                                                                                                        episode	Episode number

                                                                                                                                                                                        Query

                                                                                                                                                                                        Parameter	Values
                                                                                                                                                                                        server	sub / dub

                                                                                                                                                                                        Examples

                                                                                                                                                                                        Sub:

                                                                                                                                                                                        https://nt-animes.onrender.com/watch/naruto/1

                                                                                                                                                                                        Dub:

                                                                                                                                                                                        https://nt-animes.onrender.com/watch/naruto/1?server=dub

                                                                                                                                                                                        HTML Player Example

                                                                                                                                                                                        <video controls width="100%">
                                                                                                                                                                                          <source src="https://nt-animes.onrender.com/watch/naruto/1" type="video/mp4">
                                                                                                                                                                                          </video>


                                                                                                                                                                                          ⸻

                                                                                                                                                                                          5. Download Episode

                                                                                                                                                                                          Downloads episode as MP4.

                                                                                                                                                                                          Endpoint

                                                                                                                                                                                          GET /download/:anime/:episode

                                                                                                                                                                                          Query

                                                                                                                                                                                          Parameter	Values
                                                                                                                                                                                          server	sub / dub

                                                                                                                                                                                          Examples

                                                                                                                                                                                          Sub:

                                                                                                                                                                                          https://nt-animes.onrender.com/download/naruto/1

                                                                                                                                                                                          Dub:

                                                                                                                                                                                          https://nt-animes.onrender.com/download/naruto/1?server=dub

                                                                                                                                                                                          Downloaded File

                                                                                                                                                                                          nt-animes-{anime}-ep{episode}.mp4

                                                                                                                                                                                          Example:

                                                                                                                                                                                          nt-animes-naruto-ep1.mp4


                                                                                                                                                                                          ⸻

                                                                                                                                                                                          Typical Usage Flow

                                                                                                                                                                                          1. Search Anime

                                                                                                                                                                                          /search?keyword=naruto

                                                                                                                                                                                          2. Get anime slug

                                                                                                                                                                                          naruto

                                                                                                                                                                                          3. Fetch metadata

                                                                                                                                                                                          /metadata?anime=naruto

                                                                                                                                                                                          4. Stream episode

                                                                                                                                                                                          /watch/naruto/1

                                                                                                                                                                                          or

                                                                                                                                                                                          /watch/naruto/1?server=dub


                                                                                                                                                                                          ⸻

                                                                                                                                                                                          Notes

                                                                                                                                                                                          • Base URL:

                                                                                                                                                                                          https://nt-animes.onrender.com

                                                                                                                                                                                          • Streaming endpoint returns MP4 video stream

                                                                                                                                                                                          • Download endpoint converts HLS → MP4 automatically

                                                                                                                                                                                          • url field from search results is used as the anime slug for other endpoints.

                                                                                                                                                                                          ⸻

                                                                                                                                                                                          If you want, I can also give you a very clean developer docs version (like Stripe / OpenAI docs) that makes your API look 10× more professional.
                                                                                                                                                                                          